originalText.text: Jen has been great! I have had two laser tattoo removal sessions with her so far and she has been so comforting and patient with me through the process. It is definitely not an easy procedure but Jen has always made sure I am as comfortable as can be. Her studio is always clean and she is very professional. I will definitely be finishing my tattoo removal with her and will recommend her to others!

originalText.text:
So far, I’ve done two laser treatments on a foot tattoo I got many years ago. First thing to mention is Jennifer is an absolute sweetheart. We always chat a while we wait for the numbing cream to kick in, and Jen will share a ton of info about skincare and I always leave with so much knowledge!

As for the laser treatment itself, I wont lie and say it’s comfortable, but I have a pretty high pain tolerance and it’s over very quick! Jen has great bedside manner and will ask how I’m doing throughout and whether I’d like a break. It’s really not bad at all, to be perfectly honest.

I probably have a few sessions left but I will be coming back to get additional skincare treatments. Jen is amazing and I’m so glad I met her! :)
